Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}# 南極條約特徵 *南極洲僅用於和平目的 *自由進行科學調查和促進國際間合作 *凍結領土主權的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那裡和日本不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有許多制度和規則
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁這次集訓好好記在心裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟學校裡的你判若兩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們又不同班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼首先和隊長打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是南極觀測隊隊長藤堂吟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是女性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醜話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管隊員是隨行人員還是研究人員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都一視同仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要做的事堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你們是高中生 只要有需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無論掃地 洗衣服 苦力活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們一個都別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我的話記清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極觀測隊員有個ABC準則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A.這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}B.別做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}C.打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請把這三點謹記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:44.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\1c&H3D423E&\frz20.47\frx358\fry356\pos(336,92)}１．想活下去\N\N２．想知道更多\N\N３．想扶持隊友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:44.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\1c&H3D423E&\frx4\fry0\frz18.24\pos(-4,400)}全部符合南極觀測隊。無論如何都要活下去、生還下來。\N保持對知識和經驗的渴求。另外，不要孤立你的隊友。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她好有隊長風範啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像那種看到學生打瞌睡 就會扔粉筆的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是有考試 都是出超難的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 明天是訓練開路工程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 要去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都來山裡了 不出去走走就可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過這工程看來挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久違的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說了 對所有隊員一視同仁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒 我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子是靠自己來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過說實話 我早有預感了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從她第一次跟我說想一起去的時候起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她可是貴子的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是收發器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個是指南針
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後這個是GPS定位裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向弄懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天基本上都教過了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是為什麼要做這些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極是塊平整的大陸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用開路也能走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是平整又純白的大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦下暴風雪就會迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才要開路 方便沿著路走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪不得要插這個旗子當路標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是要插在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是要我們自己想 才有這個訓練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.19,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\pos(768,156)\frz19.15}開路工程起點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.19,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\pos(466,116)\frz20.46}通訊基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.19,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H3C3F40&\frx350\fry6\frz23.13\pos(244,446)}下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是我們目前的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:39.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frz19.15\pos(586,246)\frx348\fry356}開路工程路線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:39.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx348\fry356\frz25.21\pos(80,244)}開路工程終點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:39.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3C3F40&\frx348\fry356\frz25.21\pos(350,652)}野營訓練地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後這邊是目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到那裡去就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不單單是過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}途中的這裡 這裡和這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些地點都要插上旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別那麼隨隨便便就行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道那些地點在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…哎嘿？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賣萌也沒有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用這個一邊測量正確的地點一邊前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺會很難耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}48 49 50
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看一下角度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用右眼看還是左眼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是慣用眼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慣用眼是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我記得是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}168°
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再向右一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個右邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}緯度是這個 經度是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是比剛才的距離更遠啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果測量正確的話 應該在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那邊嗎…偏了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想起來自己當初剛參加時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他三個人是怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不清楚 其中一個原本就要參加的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知什麼時候她們變成朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他隊員說要爭取時間越短越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我覺得準確度比速度更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟安全第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}398 399 400
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向左兩步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過你居然知道小理很會用指南針啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是個直覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請叫我指南針的專家—「指南針女孩」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 我是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像畢業旅行一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不打個牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在帳篷裡睡覺也是重要的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是現在還不到8點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 隊長也說合宿的晚上要開聯歡會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快給我睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}講鬼故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有點想殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道結月害怕鬼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死請靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.53,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※結月本想説うるさい（吵死了），但這個詞對學姐講很沒禮貌，臨時改口說\N\h\h\h\h静かにしてください（請保持安靜），結果把兩個不相干的詞組在了一起。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死請靜是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你是學姐我才臨時改口的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道我想表達什麼意思就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死請靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說啦 小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直想問個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你認識隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人是媽媽高中時的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和媽媽一起去了南極
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有媽媽沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為 媽媽還等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滿天繁星 北極星是哪一顆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是在北斗七星某段的延長線上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟仙后座有關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那南極星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極星？有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是不明顯 比較難找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這裡是看不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要以為自己頭頂上的群星就是全部的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是日向的名言吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}編得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是昭和基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}極光隊能聽到嗎 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是極光隊 我是三宅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信號良好 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是定時聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有沒有異常 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本日 極光隊4名成員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人員設備均無異常 請回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破曉時溫度較低 注意保暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}定時聯絡結束 祝一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好險 差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H403533&\pos(442,280)\frz18.96}新訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H726257&\frz18.96\pos(392,354)\frx348\fry350}收件人：{\1c&H403533&}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs40\1c&H726257&\frz18.96\frx348\fry350\pos(548,506)}主旨：{\1c&H403533&}致媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨的媽媽是怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我只能回答你 她是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像報瀨那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 我不清楚她女兒是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過她們的執著與死心眼 倒是像極了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真夠麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:26.49,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}深夜零時の地平線　広がる世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:30.95,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今日がずっと眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:41.72,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}鼻の奥がツンとした　きれいできれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:46.34,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}胸が痛くなるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:55.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}両手いっぱいありったけの人に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:06.57,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}意味なんかないって言われ続けたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:19.13,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}宇宙(そら)から届くひかり　逆さまの星空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:23.17,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:31.72,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さあ　迷いなんて置き去りにして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:38.31,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}探しに行くんだ　見果てぬ世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:46.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さあ前を向いて　間違いなかったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:53.33,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}言ってやるんだ　この思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:22:01.80,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}勇気出して　進んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:26.49,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}眼前是深夜零點的地平線 一片廣大的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:30.95,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今天一直是那麼耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:41.72,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我激動得鼻尖一癢 眼前的景象是那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:46.34,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}燦爛到叫我心口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:55.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}許許多多的人 裝滿雙手也擠不下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:06.57,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}都在勸我不要白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:19.13,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}只是仰頭看見那顛倒的星空 灑下的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:23.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我會從這裡揚帆起航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:31.72,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}把心裡的迷茫留在岸邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:38.31,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}去探索廣闊無垠 斑斕神秘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:46.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}睜大眼睛直視前方 大聲喊出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:53.33,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}「我的執著沒有錯誤！」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:22:01.80,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}拿出勇氣 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但麻煩點才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的性格很適合去南極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要去南極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被她叫來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是下決心的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想和她一起去 不想就這樣虛度高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想去見識不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過認識了日向和結月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了觀測隊隊員的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽了隊長和報瀨的事情後 我才覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是哪裡都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是非南極不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和大家一起去南極
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早起很難受的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了快起來 還有報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想和大家一起找到南極星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看極光 吃刨冰 和企鵝拍紀念照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一定要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Comment: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:25.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:36.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:42.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:53.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:23:04.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:15.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:20.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:25.86,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:36.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:42.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:53.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:23:04.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:15.37,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:20.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H8AA4A0&\pos(234,68)\frz13.84}好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H838D8B&\frz13.84\pos(662,660)}這裡很美吧？
